DAFTAR TIPE DATA YANG ADA DI BAHASA C++

====================================================================================================
|     NAMA TIPE DATA     |  UKURAN DALAM MEMORI  |                  RENTANG NILAI                  |
====================================================================================================
|        integer         |        4 bytes        |         -2147483648 sampai 2147483647           |
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|         float          |        4 bytes        |          3.4 * 10-38 hingga 3.4 * 1038          |
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|         double         |        8 bytes        |         1.7 * 10-308 hingga 1.7 * 10308         |
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|          char          |        1 bytes        |        -127 sampai 127 atau 0 sampai 255        |
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|        boolean         |        4 bytes        |                true atau false                  |
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|       short int        |        2 bytes        |              -32768 sampai 32767                |
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|       long int         |        4 bytes        |      -2,147,483,648 sampai 2,147,483,647        |
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|        string          |                       |                                                 |
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
